Use Tap919 Middleman as the payroll engine: you’re not running a “promo affiliate program,” you’re turning people into metered **field reps** that your system can track and pay like on‑demand employees. [payproglobal](https://payproglobal.com/answers/what-is-saas-affiliate-program/)

Below is a concrete, agent‑ready affiliate system you can bolt onto what we’ve already built.

